"Even this week Hamas attempted to violate the agreement and > create a false crisis with false accusations," said Netanyahu, according to the Israeli media.<br> The release of the hostages, > explained, is due to the support of US President Donald Trump and the "concentration of our forces in the Strip and the clear and unequivocal statements of President Trump".<br> Now "we are working in full co-ordination with the United States to free all our hostages, alive and dead as soon as possible, and we are preparing with the utmost intensity for what will come next, in all senses," warned Netanyahu.
